---
// Components
// - Layout
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

// - SEO
const SEO = {
title: 'Privacy Policy | Activate Your Voice',
description:
'Our privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information at Activate Your Voice.'
}
---

<Layout title={SEO.title} description={SEO.description}>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<div style="position:relative;width:100vw;max-width:100%;overflow:hidden;height:320px;">
<img src="/presentation.jpg" alt="Privacy banner" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;" />
<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(229,231,235,0.5);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(6px);"></div>
<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:1rem;">
<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-4">Privacy <span class="text-primary-500">Policy</span></h1>
<p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-neutral-700 text-center max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
How we protect your data.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="post-body basic-text basic-text--lg">
<h3>Who we are</h3>
<p>Our website address is: <a href="https://www.activateyourvoice.co.uk" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">https://www.activateyourvoice.co.uk</a></p>

<h3>What personal data we collect and why we collect it</h3>

<h4>Contact Forms & Feedback</h4>
<p>We use contact and feedback forms to collect information necessary to respond to your inquiries and improve our services. This includes your name, email address, phone number, the tutor you are inquiring about, and the type of tuition. This data is handled with strict confidentiality and stored securely via our hosting provider, Netlify.</p>

<h4>reCAPTCHA</h4>
<p>To protect our forms from spam and abuse, we use Google reCAPTCHA v2. This service collects hardware and software information, such as device and application data, and sends it to Google for analysis. The information collected in connection with your use of reCAPTCHA will be used for improving reCAPTCHA and for general security purposes; it will not be used for personalized advertising by Google. Your use of reCAPTCHA is subject to the Google <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">Terms of Use</a>.</p>

<h4>Analytics</h4>
<p>We use Google Analytics and Google Tag Manager to understand how visitors interact with our website. These tools use cookies to collect standard internet log information and visitor behavior information in an anonymous form. This helps us compile statistical reports on activity and improve the website experience.</p>

<h4>Calendly</h4>
<p>We use Calendly to facilitate easy booking for consultations. When you use Calendly on our site, you may be provided to provide your name and email. This data is governed by <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">Calendly's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

<h4>Cookies</h4>
<p>Our website uses cookies to personalize your experience, track visitor usage, and compile statistical reports. You can set your browser not to accept cookies; however, some website features may not function as a result. For further information, visit <a href="http://www.allaboutcookies.org/" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">http://www.allaboutcookies.org/</a>.</p>

<h3>How long we retain your data</h3>
<p>We retain info provided through our contact and feedback forms for as long as necessary to provide you with the requested services and to comply with legal and administrative requirements.</p>

<h3>Who we share your data with</h3>
<p>We do not sell your personal data. We share information with trusted third parties who perform services on our behalf (such as Netlify for form hosting, and Google for analytics and reCAPTCHA) or to comply with legal obligations.</p>

<h3>What rights you have over your data</h3>
<p>You can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, or request that we erase any personal data. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>

<h3>Usage of Personal Information</h3>
<p>Activate Your Voice will only use your personal information to:</p>
<ul class="list-disc marker:text-primary-500 ml-6 space-y-2">
<li>Administer and manage our relationship with you;</li>
<li>To deal with any enquiries or feedback we receive from you;</li>
<li>To comply with applicable laws, regulations and rules;</li>
<li>To notify you of changes to what we do;</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-8">We may disclose your personal information to third parties in other circumstances, in particular:</p>
<ul class="list-disc marker:text-primary-500 ml-6 space-y-2">
<li>Third parties that perform services on our behalf;</li>
<li>To protect the rights, property or safety of Activate Your Voice, our staff, customers, or others;</li>
<li>If we are under a duty to disclose or share your personal information, to comply with any legal obligations;</li>
<li>Fraud sharing organisations; and in response to a request from a governmental authority.</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-8">We will not keep your personal information longer than is necessary, taking into account legal requirements and limitation periods.</p>

<p>If you have any queries about how we use your personal information, please contact us at any time via e-mail.</p>
<p>To obtain a copy of our full privacy notice please e-mail <a href="mailto:info@activateyourvoice.co.uk" class="text-primary-500 hover:underline">info@activateyourvoice.co.uk</a>.</p>
</div>
</Layout>

<style>
.post-body {
@apply mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-10 pb-12 lg:pb-24;
}
</style>

